    "description": "<i>We have lost contact with the Arch-Phrenic. <br>The vicious forest, Chedone, stirs. <br>We have no Guildmaster, and my father is dead. <br>The Cheds are coming. <br>Diichohhs , send your strongest Crusaders……<br>We must discover the secret of Chedone…..<br><br>-Letter from Gaz’ra-Lina, <br> Thilo-t’ess of Kilhellos, to the <br>Crusader Diichohhs</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/0c92271bf695071c8a40097df317f0a2.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=300 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/0c92271bf695071c8a40097df317f0a2.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/0c92271bf695071c8a40097df317f0a2.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>**About this Game **</strong><br><br><i>*Ahh Barquay, you have come. Sit by the fire, stay a moment, and listen to your father. <br>You have lived a life of peace and comfort, <br>As much as one can in the shadow of Chedone. <br>But the time has come, my son. <br>I can no longer protect you. <br>I have not raised a hilo’ness in this house!  <br>Diichohhs has sounded the horn. <br>He calls all able bodied men to Chedone, <br>To find the source of this mystery. <br>You will do what I could not Barquay…….*</i><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><strong>**Turtle River is a punishing,  loot-based, JRPG pixel art dungeon crawler.**</strong><br><br>You are Husio Barquay, a literal wallflower who has never taken a risk or faced serious danger in his life. <br><br>Until the Crusader Prophet Diichohhs called upon all Turtillian men of fighting age to enter the vicious forest of Chedone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/a226dabed60918cbc5c77193a31f15da.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/a226dabed60918cbc5c77193a31f15da.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/a226dabed60918cbc5c77193a31f15da.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>**JRPG meets ARPG **</strong><br><br>Slay hordes upon hordes of enemies in this fast - paced Active Time Battle JRPG. <br><br>Terrifying Elites, Suffocating Swarms, and Ball-Crushing Bosses await your blade. <br><br>Inspired by classic ARPG loot games, in a JRPG package.<br><br><strong>**Punishing, rewarding combat. **</strong><br><br>Chedone is no joke friend. You’ll need all your tactical wits and fast reflexes to defeat the Ched hordes. <br><br>Frequent status ailments, stuns, and traps will leave the taste of death fresh in your mouth. <br><br>Failure will give no rewards, except the gift of knowledge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/f0a9c8fa45c562c1acb84220432cc3c1.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/f0a9c8fa45c562c1acb84220432cc3c1.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/f0a9c8fa45c562c1acb84220432cc3c1.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>** 3 Classic Classes **</strong><br><br>Play as the weapon wielding Barbarian,  Gun-Bow  blasting Ranger, or the  Potion-Pelting Herbologist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/fd01bff57295fe1bb0baa7ce64038870.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/fd01bff57295fe1bb0baa7ce64038870.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/fd01bff57295fe1bb0baa7ce64038870.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>**Build your own Barquay **</strong><br><br>Freedom to build your character, your way. <br>Master multiple skills and builds for each class, wield different weapons and armors. <br>Will you be a summoner-warrior? A Nuker Mage? A Debuff Archer? A Living tree? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/e15a55579806478652a251aa170bff75.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/e15a55579806478652a251aa170bff75.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/e15a55579806478652a251aa170bff75.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9427cca5a48b2855ed3255c1dc6633ad.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9427cca5a48b2855ed3255c1dc6633ad.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9427cca5a48b2855ed3255c1dc6633ad.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>**Shower yourself in Loot **</strong><br><br>Wield build-changing Unique weapons, or craft yourself the perfect set of armor with the crafting system. <br><br>Wield multiple weapons simultaneously  and swap between them instantly before each attack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9d4e746b876d85a4dca1b4fafc878039.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9d4e746b876d85a4dca1b4fafc878039.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/9d4e746b876d85a4dca1b4fafc878039.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/40bb24fbc05e0a61d44066d8f0899ec2.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/40bb24fbc05e0a61d44066d8f0899ec2.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/40bb24fbc05e0a61d44066d8f0899ec2.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>**A modern JRPG experience **</strong><br><br>Full pixel movement.<br>No random encounters, no long drawn out story scenes. <br>Easy to sort inventory, modern UI, and fast paced, interaction based combat. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/7a9c3a47c8ebb210ec0662d062e4c414.poster.avif?t=1724687247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/7a9c3a47c8ebb210ec0662d062e4c414.webm?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010800/extras/7a9c3a47c8ebb210ec0662d062e4c414.mp4?t=1724687247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>**No Procedural Generation**</strong><br><br>Every event, piece of gear, and line of dialogue was hand crafted by a passionate developer.<br><br>Aside from loot drops, there is very little randomization. <br><br><strong>**Forge your way through the Forest **</strong><br><br>Multiple paths await you in Chedone. <br>Will you take the long, safe path? Or the Gauntlet? <br><br>Try a new class or build in the New Game + Mode",
